quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,7,"By the heaven containing pathways,<sup foot_note=197414>1</sup>",footnotes:197414:1
  51,8,"Indeed, you are in differing speech.<sup foot_note=197415>1</sup>",footnotes:197415:1
  51,9,"Deluded away from it [i.e., the Qur’ān] is he who is deluded."
  51,10,"Destroyed are the misinformers<sup foot_note=197416>1</sup>",footnotes:197416:1